text: Rado Istenič (born 18 August 1915, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
